						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">No date</hi></p>						

						<p>States that <hi rend="bold">Uttama-Nambirāya,</hi> the brother of <hi rend="bold">Chakrarāya,</hi> obtained from Prauḍha Dēvarāya (I) several honours like the royal umbrella, ornaments, vehicles, etc., and the proprietory rights of administration in the temple. The record is in Sanskrit in Grantha characters.</p>						

